// TextRenderer on MLC (TRACK_TEXT_RENDERING_NATIVE STEP=5).
// GlyphAtlas shelf pack + GlyphCache LRU + textured quad batching via dispatch.
// Synthetic A8 atlas glyphs (solid rects); FreeType/HarfBuzz wired in STEP=6 demo.

